General.Name: Cann Group Ltd
General.Description: Cann Group Limited engages in the breeding, cultivation, production, manufacturing, clinical evaluation, and supplying medicinal cannabis for sale and use within Australia and for overseas export markets. It licenses to undertake research and to cultivate cannabis for human medicinal and research purposes. The company was founded in 2014 and is based in Port Melbourne, Australia.
